## Functional Requirements

### 4.1 Authentication

- Email registration and login
- Forgot password with email reset flow
- Social login (Google/Apple as platform supports)
- Biometric login (local auth wrapper over existing session)
- **Acceptance:** Secure login; password reset emails deliver successfully

### 4.2 Dashboard

Display: total assets, active warranties, expiring warranties, maintenance reminders, recently added items.  
**Performance:** Load within **3 seconds**.

### 4.3 Asset Management

**Required fields:** Item Name, Category  
**Optional fields:** Brand, Model Number, Serial Number, Purchase Date, Purchase Price, Room Location, Description

**Categories (enum):** Electronics, Furniture, Appliances, Jewelry, Tools, Vehicles, Office Equipment, Other

**Operations:** Add, Edit, Delete, View Details, Duplicate Asset

```dart
// Asset model must include at minimum:
// id, name, category, createdAt, updatedAt, userId
// Optional: brand, modelNumber, serialNumber, purchaseDate, purchasePrice, room, description
```

### 4.4 Barcode Scanner

- Scan barcode → lookup product database → auto-fill asset fields when found
- **Acceptance:** Scan completes within **2 seconds**; auto-populate when data available

### 4.5 Photo Management

- Multiple images per asset; capture or upload
- Compress images before upload
- Store in Firebase Storage with local cache/SQLite metadata

### 4.6 Warranty Management

Store: start date, expiry date, provider, warranty documents.  
**Notifications:** 90, 30, and 7 days before expiry (FCM + local scheduling fallback).

### 4.7 Receipt Storage

- Upload PDF, JPG, PNG
- Store receipt number and purchase details
- OCR (optional/premium): extract store name, purchase date, amount

### 4.8 Maintenance Tracker

- Recurring or one-time maintenance schedules (HVAC, vehicle, filters, etc.)
- Push reminders before due date

### 4.9 Insurance Vault

- Store policies, coverage details, claim documents
- Link assets to policies (many-to-many relationship)

### 4.10 Search & Filter

**Search:** asset name, category, brand, serial number  
**Filters:** room, purchase year, warranty status, asset value  
**Performance:** Results within **1 second**

### 4.11 Reports

| Report | Contents | Export |
|--------|----------|--------|
| Insurance Report | Asset details, photos, estimated value | PDF, Excel |
| Home Asset Report | Total count, total value | PDF, Excel |

### 4.12 Notifications

Push notifications for: warranty expiration, maintenance due, document expiration.

### 4.13 Cloud Backup

Automatic backup, manual backup, and restore — sync Firestore + Storage with local SQLite cache.

