## AI Features (Premium — gate behind subscription)

| Feature | Behavior |
|---------|----------|
| AI Asset Recognition | Photo → identify product type, brand, category |
| AI Value Estimation | Current market value and depreciation |
| AI Receipt Reader | Extract store, product, price, purchase date |

Do not block MVP core flows on AI; implement as optional premium modules.

---

## Non-Functional Requirements

| Area | Target |
|------|--------|
| App startup | < 3 seconds |
| Dashboard load | < 3 seconds |
| Search | < 1 second |
| Security | JWT auth, encrypted data at rest/transit, secure cloud storage, biometric login |
| Scalability | 100,000+ users, millions of assets |
| Availability | 99.9% uptime (Firebase SLA + graceful offline degradation) |

**Offline-first:** Use SQLite for local cache; sync with Firestore when online.

---

## MVP Scope vs Future (Do Not Implement Unless Asked)

**Future enhancements — out of MVP scope:**

- Family sharing, asset lending tracker, smart home integration
- QR code labels, voice assistant, web dashboard
- Multi-language support, used-item marketplace

