## Implementation Checklist

Before marking a feature complete:

- [ ] Matches SRS acceptance criteria and performance targets
- [ ] Uses bloc + Clean Architecture folder structure
- [ ] Repository pattern with Firestore/SQLite/Storage abstraction
- [ ] Required asset fields validated; categories use enum
- [ ] Images compressed before upload
- [ ] Notifications scheduled for warranty/maintenance thresholds
- [ ] Search/filter indexed for sub-1s response
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets; use Firebase config and environment variables
- [ ] Widget tests for complex UI; unit tests for blocs and use cases


## 🎨 5. Theming and Styling Rules

