| Purpose     | Constant                      |
|-------------|-------------------------------|
| Colors      | `HimColors`                   |
| Font Size   | `FontSizes`                   |
| Padding     | `Dimensions`                  |
| Spacing     | `Dimensions`                  |
| Sizes       | `Dimensions`                  |
